The [[Protocol Guild]], by Trent:

"the Guild was structured to facilitate funding with the lowest bureaucratic overhead possible imposed on members. At its core are two very basic primitives, which are present in all funding allocation mechanisms.

* a curation process which produces a list of eligible recipients

* a weighting mechanism applied to that list."

